div.font: This model will be a AI agent with real time processing capibalities. it will take a request from the user using speech, then it will scan the area for text and objects using the camera while asking the CV model questions from the user input to get the maximum context from the image plus any text the OCR can pickup. It will then add all 3 of these inputs the users origial question plus the image context and image text to then generate a structured promt for the LLM giving it as much context and details as possible before we use its output to be returned to the user to answer there question. This output is read back to the user as speach using text to speach.
